1
00:00:00,652 --> 00:00:02,414
Ow!
Ow!

2
00:00:02,663 --> 00:00:05,720
What's the matter, Andy?
怎么了,Andy?

3
00:00:05,721 --> 00:00:09,332
I slipped and fell downstairs.
我滑了一跤,从楼梯上摔下来了.

4
00:00:09,429 --> 00:00:12,313
Have you hurt yourself?
你摔伤了自己吗?

5
00:00:12,314 --> 00:00:18,530
Yes, I have. I think that I've hurt my back.
是的,摔伤了.我想我把背摔坏了.

6
00:00:18,531 --> 00:00:21,293
Try and stand up.
试试站起来.

7
00:00:21,294 --> 00:00:23,772
Can you stand up?
你能站起来吗?

8
00:00:23,773 --> 00:00:26,738
Here. Let me help you.
来,让我帮你.

9
00:00:26,739 --> 00:00:28,906
I'm sorry, Lucy.
对不起,Lucy,

10
00:00:29,608 --> 00:00:34,485
I think that the doctor had better see you.
我想最好请医生来给你看一下.

11
00:00:34,486 --> 00:00:37,659
I'll phone Dr. Carter.
我去给Carter医生打电话.

12
00:00:38,177 --> 00:00:43,014
The doctor says that he will come at once.
医生说他马上就来.

13
00:00:43,230 --> 00:00:48,368
I'm sure that you need an X-ray, Andy.
Andy,我看你需要做一次X光透视.


